metadata.name: Golden Birds
metadata.description:
This photograph depicts one of the most emblematic bridges in the world, the Golden Gate Bridge.

Lovely color tones with the blue sky and the marvelous sunset during a September evening. The color of the bridge is a unique version of the "International Orange" used in aerospace industry.

Artist : Pierre-Louis Missler
Year of Creation : 2018
Place : San Francisco, CA
Edition : 1/1
Size : 6000 px on the long end
